ai known only as 'Jack' is running out of hope. Will anyone come to his aid or is this the end of his lifelong mission? <ref>[http://www.atomicempire.com/issue.aspx?cover=113789& Issue 13]: [[Samurai Jack]] - Released: October, 2014 (On [http://www.atomicempire.com atomicempire.com])</ref>||October 22, 2014\n|-\n| 14||The Quest of the Broken Blade: Part Four||Jack is tested by power greater than any he has ever faced before. Can he prove himself worthy and regain his strength?<ref>[http://www.atomicempire.com/issue.aspx?cover=114900& Issue 14]: [[Samurai Jack]] - Released: November, 2014 (On [http://www.atomicempire.com atomicempire.com])</ref>||November 30, 2014\n|-\n| 15||The Quest of the Broken Blade: Part Five||Jack faces Aku in one-on-one combat and both are determined to make it their final battle. Past and present collide in this epic conclusion to the 'Quest of the Broken Blade' storyline.<ref>[http://www.atomicempire.com/issue.aspx?cover=115959& Issue 15]: [[Samurai Jack]] - Released: December, 2014 (On [http://www.atomicempire.com atomicempire.com])</ref>||December 31, 2014\n|-\n| 16||The Master of Time: Part One||A prophet calling himself the \"Master of Time\" hides within a compound crawling with untold monsters and deadly traps. Jack the Samurai will need to become Jack the Infiltrator if he hopes to gain an audience with the mysterious master.<ref>[http://www.comicvine.com/samurai-jack-16-samurai-jack-and-the-master-of-tim/4000-476813/ Issue 16]: [[Samurai Jack]] - Released: January, 2015 (On [http://www.comicvine.com comicvine.com])</ref>||January 31, 2015\n|-\n| 17||The Master of Time: Part Two||Jack and the Thief team-up to discover the mysteries of the secretive man known only as the \u201cMaster of Time.\u201d Is this finally the way home for our solemn samurai?<ref>[http://www.idwpublishing.com/product/samurai-jack-17/ Issue 17]: [[Samurai Jack]] - Released: February, 2015 (On [http://idwpublishing.com idwpublishing.com])</ref>||February 28, 201